    "shortDescription": "<p>You automatically detect and locate conscious creatures within 60 feet, as if you possessed the blindsight ability. <i>Nondetection</i>, <i>mind blank</i>, and similar effects can block this effect. <i>Thoughtsense</i> can distinguish between sentient (Intelligence 3 or greater) and non-sentient (Intelligence 1-2) creatures, but otherwise provides no information about the creatures it detects.</p>"
